---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="footer__cta panel" data-reveal>
      <div>
        <h2 class="footer__ctaTitle">Start your <span class="nb">GLP-1</span> plan with real information.</h2>
        <p class="prose">A clear read on your own biology, ready for your next clinician visit.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="#enroll" class="btn">Get your protocol<span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer__main">
      <a href="#main" class="brand">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true" width="26" height="26">
          <path d="M4 20 L11 20 L14 8 L18 24 L21 14 L24 14 L27 11"
                fill="none" stroke="var(--jade)" stroke-width="2.2"
                stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
          <circle cx="21" cy="14" r="2.2" fill="var(--jade)"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Balance Protocol <span style="color:var(--jade)">GPS</span></span>
      </a>
      <p class="footer__tag">
        A systems-biology program fusing functional biomarkers, clinically relevant
        genetics, and expert interpretation, powered by NutraCoreX™.
      </p>
    </div>

    <hr class="hr" />

    <section class="footer__notes" id="disclaimer" aria-label="Important disclaimers">
      <h2 class="footer__notesTitle">Important information</h2>
      <ol class="footer__noteList">
        <li id="note-1">
          <span class="footer__noteNum">1.</span>
          <span>Balance Protocol™ GPS and NutraCoreX™ are wellness and laboratory testing
          services. They are not a GLP-1 medication, a prescription, or a pharmacy, and they
          do not guarantee weight loss or any specific health outcome. Results from GLP-1
          medications vary from person to person and depend on factors including diet,
          activity, lifestyle, and individual medical history.</span>
        </li>
        <li id="note-2">
          <span class="footer__noteNum">2.</span>
          <span>This service does not prescribe medication, diagnose conditions, or replace
          care from a licensed healthcare provider. Test results are intended to give you and
          your own clinician additional context. All decisions about starting, dosing,
          continuing, or stopping any medication, including GLP-1 medications, must be made
          with a qualified healthcare professional. Never start or change a medication based
          on this report alone.</span>
        </li>
        <li id="note-3">
          <span class="footer__noteNum">3.</span>
          <span>The $998 price covers one NutraCoreX™ at-home collection kit and its report.
          Practitioner support is optional and offered without pressure. Ships
          internationally; additional FedEx charges may apply outside the United States.
          Results are typically available 10 to 14 business days after the lab receives your
          samples.</span>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <p class="footer__disclaimer">
        NutraCoreX™ provides wellness insights based on functional biomarkers and targeted
        genetic variations. Health outcomes depend on multiple factors, including lifestyle,
        diet, and environment. These statements have not been evaluated by the Food and Drug
        Administration. This test is not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any
        disease. Individual results may vary. Always consult a qualified healthcare
        professional before making any health or medication decision. If you experience a
        medical emergency, call your local emergency number.
      </p>
      <p class="footer__disclaimer">
        Privacy: laboratory analysis is performed by Genova Diagnostics, which does not retain
        your DNA or personal health data beyond delivering your results. Your information is
        never sold.
      </p>
    </section>

    <p class="footer__legal">
      © {year} Balance Protocol™ GPS. All rights reserved. Lab services by Genova Diagnostics.
      Balance Protocol™, GPS, and NutraCoreX™ are trademarks of their respective owner.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  .footer { background: var(--ink-deep); padding-block: var(--sp-7) var(--sp-6); border-top: 1px solid var(--line-soft); }
  .footer__cta {
    display: grid; gap: var(--sp-4); align-items: center;
    padding: var(--sp-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-7);
    background:
      radial-gradient(90% 140% at 90% 0%, oklch(28% 0.05 162 / 0.6), transparent 60%),
      var(--surface);
  }
  .footer__ctaTitle { font-size: var(--step-2); margin-bottom: var(--sp-2); }
  @media (min-width: 760px) {
    .footer__cta { grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: var(--sp-6); }
  }

  .footer__main { display: grid; gap: var(--sp-3); margin-bottom: var(--sp-5); }
  .brand { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem; font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .footer__tag { color: var(--muted-2); max-width: 52ch; font-size: var(--step--1); }
  @media (min-width: 760px) {
    .footer__main { grid-template-columns: auto 1fr; align-items: center; gap: var(--sp-6); }
  }

  .footer__notes { margin-top: var(--sp-5); scroll-margin-top: 90px; }
  .footer__notesTitle {
    font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: var(--step--1); font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--sp-3);
  }
  .footer__noteList { display: grid; gap: var(--sp-3); max-width: 92ch; }
  .footer__noteList li {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1.4rem 1fr; gap: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--muted-2); font-size: var(--step--1); line-height: 1.55;
  }
  .footer__noteList li:target { color: var(--muted); }
  .footer__noteNum { color: var(--jade); font-weight: 600; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums; }

  .footer__disclaimer { color: var(--muted-2); font-size: var(--step--1); line-height: 1.55; max-width: 92ch; margin-top: var(--sp-4); }
  .footer__legal { color: var(--muted-2); font-size: var(--step--1); margin-top: var(--sp-4); }
</style>
